#CHIP YM2608
#CLOCK 7987200

; YM2608 (OPNA) SSG Channels Test — 3× PSG channels
;
; The YM2608 integrates Yamaha's SSG (Square/Sawtooth/Noise) synthesizer,
; identical to the AY8910/YM2149 PSG chips.
;
; Tests SSG channels:
; - Square wave tone
; - Envelope modulation
; - Noise synthesis

#TRACK 0

TEMPO 120

; SSG Channel 1: Square wave
c4 . d4 . e4 .

r4

; SSG Channel 2: With envelope decay
f4 . . g4 . .

r4

; SSG Channel 3: Noise
r4 . . .

r4

r2

#END
